        <name>AI Council Assessment</name>
        <styleUrl>#intel</styleUrl>
        <description>The current military posture and activity patterns suggest a high level of activity in support of Operation Epic Fury, with multiple aircraft conducting transport, ISR, and patrol operations. The USNS Effective is deployed in the Pacific, likely supporting the operation. The US military is also conducting exercises and training operations, including the African Land Forces Summit and Exercise Cobra Gold 2026. The F-22 Raptor &#39;2.0&#39; is undergoing flight testing, and the Army&#39;s revamped system for getting gear and weapons to the fight faster has been put into use in support of Operation Epic Fury. The US military is maintaining a high level of readiness and activity, with a focus on supporting Operation Epic Fury and preparing for potential future conflicts. The alliance between the US and Thailand is being strengthened through military engagements, and the Oregon Military Department&#39;s 2026 Innovation Summit is leveraging innovative approaches for warfighting challenges. Overall, the US military is demonstrating its capabilities and commitment to regional security through a range of operations and exercises.</description>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>0,0,0</coordinates>
        </Point>
